<plot>Fatima is a young British Muslim woman of Moroccan origin who ran away from her family and now shares a house with two girlfriends in Tottenham. One morning she receives a call from someone claiming to be from the Police. He tells her that there will be a visit later that day to her house to interview her, but refuses to tell her why. Set in London during the emotional and political aftermath of the recent war and occupation of Iraq, THE WINTER SUN IS A LIE is an Award Winning quirky drama about lies and liars.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?601446</url></doc>
